Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:30.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:89152,90528}I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.52,0:01:31.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:90528,91946}Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.32,0:01:34.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:93323,94407}Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.24,0:01:40.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:99245,100663}Thank you, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:45.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:100663,105668}You thought I forgot\Nmy school bag, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:48.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:105668,108296}The thing is, I don't need it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:51.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:108671,111674}Today we're going for a trip\Noutside the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:54.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111674,114510}Look, this is my lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:58.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:114802,118348}So today you don't have to\Nwalk me to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.60,0:02:07.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:125605,127440}You want to tag along?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.73,0:02:14.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:132737,134489}Is everyone ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.48,0:02:15.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:134489,135698}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:18.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:136240,138951}Listen, Lassie.\NWait for my sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:20.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:138951,140703}What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:23.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:141996,143206}Hey, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:25.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:143206,145458}Lassie's seeing you off\Ntoday as well, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:26.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:145458,146793}Yes. That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:29.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147168,149295}You can enter, one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:31.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149671,151297}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:33.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:151839,153925}Being a wife is not so easy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:37.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153925,157804}You just married him, and he's already\Ntaking you on his school trips.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:39.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157804,159847}To be honest, I like it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:44.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:161933,164560}Everyone is on the cart, right?\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:48.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167105,168064}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:52.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170108,172235}We're leaving, children!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:55.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172235,175571}Make sure not to fall out\Nfrom the cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:56.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175571,176572}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:59.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:176989,179409}– We're all set, let's go.\N– Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:08.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:186040,188209}Come on, Lassie. Hop on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:13.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191796,193172}Here, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:22.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:200972,202223}Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:26.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204434,206227}Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:58.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:235006,238342}Children, after we get off the cart,\Nwe are going to board this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:04:00.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238342,240470}I'll go talk to the guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:01.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240470,241763}I have the tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:04.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243264,244307}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:05.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244307,245808}You can step off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:06.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245808,246768}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:11.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250646,251856}Thank you, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:13.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:251856,253107}See you when we get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:15.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:253107,255985}Sure… Be careful…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:20.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258821,260156}Lassie, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:22.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261574,262408}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:51.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288559,291312}We managed to get her\Non board, but what next?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:54.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291312,294315}I wonder if there's anywhere\Nwe could hide her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:56.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294315,296359}John, it's Mr. Curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:57.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:296359,297235}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:59.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297235,299237}Colin, take care of Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:02.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:301239,302532}Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:04.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302532,304617}What's the matter,\NJohn Carraclough?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:06.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304617,306577}Well… Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:09.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:307537,309205}I have a question!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:09.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309205,309872}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:13.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310540,313125}Where to hide Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:26.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325054,326556}Definitely not this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:34.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333563,334814}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:41.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:339569,341404}Thank you, doggie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:42.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:341404,342738}Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:44.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342738,344365}Ah, you're…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:48.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346993,348160}My hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:53.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351038,353875}Geez, that was my favorite hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:55.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:353875,355918}I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:01.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359505,361549}There's no recovering it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:03.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361549,363009}I'll forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:09.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:367597,369807}Right. I have to hide Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:11.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369807,371142}– Hide?\N– Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:13.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:372351,373936}I know a good place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:14.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373936,374812}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:19.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375563,379233}I see. If you're going to the Skull Peninsula,\Nwe're headed in the same direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:21.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379233,381152}The same direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:27.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381152,387992}Yes. But there I'll going to board another\Nbig ship, bound all the way for Australia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:30.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:387992,390828}My father went before me\Nand now he is waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:32.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391412,392872}You're a foreigner…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:35.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392872,395291}I'd like to travel abroad some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:42.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:400546,402089}So what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:43.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402089,403174}Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.17,0:06:45.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403174,405259}You silly.\NI'm asking about your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:47.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406802,407845}Colin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:49.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:408220,409639}I'm Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:50.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409639,410848}Nice to meet you, Colin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:53.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412433,413851}Nice to meet you, Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:56.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414518,416145}Nice to meet you, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:04.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421943,424695}What was that\Npiece of paper before?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:06.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424695,426864}It seemed really important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:09.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426864,429992}It's a treasure map.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:11.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429992,431077}A treasure map?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:20.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435873,440920}Once I get to the Skull Peninsula,\NI'm going to look for a treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:22.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440920,442713}Can I go with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:23.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442713,443255}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:26.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443255,446676}It's to make up\Nfor the hat that you lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:28.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446676,448844}Do you want to join us, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:40.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458479,460064}Colin Jones?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:43.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:460940,463776}Colin Jones is missing.\NDid anyone see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:47.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464360,467530}Shall I look for him\Non the ship once more?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:49.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:467530,469865}This is bad.\NHe can't simply leave the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:52.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469865,472034}Right. He can't leave Lassie alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:55.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:473035,475579}What if he fell into the sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:01.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:479375,481502}Colin! La—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:04.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481502,484338}You wouldn't have brought\NLassie here, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:06.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:484338,486173}Ah… Of course not…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:07.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486173,487842}Sir, I have a question!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:09.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:487842,489552}Save it for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:12.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:490428,492596}I'm sorry I'm late, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:14.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:492596,494056}Colin, how will you\Nexplain this dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:17.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495224,497351}What's wrong with Sebastian?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:18.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:497351,498561}Sebastian?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:20.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498561,500062}Is that this dog's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:21.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500396,501605}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:24.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501605,504316}Say hello to them, Sebastian.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:27.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506027,507194}What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:28.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507194,508154}I'm Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:30.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508154,510239}We met on the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:32.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510239,512533}Fair enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:36.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:512533,516328}Now that we're all gathered,\Nwe'll have a lunch in the lighthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:37.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516328,517913}We're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:38.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517913,518873}Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:42.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:520958,522710}What's going on, Colin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:46.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523878,526714}Hello, John.\NHello, Sandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:49.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527131,529175}I'm Chris.\NNice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:51.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:529175,531427}I heard about you from Colin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.42,0:08:53.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531427,533721}It was a pretty good plan,\Ndon't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:54.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:533721,534680}Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:56.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534680,536390}Hello, Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:09:00.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536390,540603}We thought Lassie would stay\Nwith her until we had free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:01.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540603,541228}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:02.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541228,542521}That's quite smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:05.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:542980,545024}I'll wait for you near the peninsula.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:06.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:545274,546025}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:07.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546025,547568}Take care of Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:09.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:547568,549528}Let's go, Sebastian.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:11.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:550654,551530}Oh, just a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:14.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:552490,554241}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:15.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554241,555743}It's Lassie's lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:17.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:556285,557495}Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:19.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557495,559497}See you at the peninsula.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:21.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:560081,561957}– See you, Chris!\N– Something doesn't sit right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:22.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:561957,562750}It must be her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:25.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563084,565252}Hey! Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:32.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:568589,572968}Even if I suddenly shout her name,\Nit didn't turn back. Must be some other dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:41.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579433,581477}It's so nice to listen\Nto the sea, Robert.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:43.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:581769,583020}I wanna go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:43.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583020,583938}Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:46.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583938,586482}A treasure hunt…\NSo exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:587274,588984}It's on that island?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:51.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:588984,591487}It's not an island\Nif we can get there on foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:52.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591487,592905}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:54.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:592905,594907}We'll look for treasure\Nduring our free time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:56.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594907,596617}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:58.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597493,598494}Colin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:09:59.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598744,599954}Children!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:03.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599954,603916}In the afternoon,\Nyou can go down to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:05.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603916,605793}But make sure\Nnot to go too far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:08.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605793,608963}In particular, any trips\Nto that island are strictly forbidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:10.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609421,610131}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:11.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610131,611298}Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:13.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611924,613968}He says we can't go to the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:15.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613968,615261}I wonder why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:25.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:623561,625312}– Did we make you wait?\N– No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:27.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:625312,627898}– Here, I'm returning Lassie.\N– Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:31.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628315,631902}John, I'm going\Nwith Chris, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:33.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632736,633904}But the teacher said…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:36.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:634572,636949}Colin, I don't want to force you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:38.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636949,638117}I can go by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:39.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638117,639410}No. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:41.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:639910,641912}I really want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:43.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:642621,643831}Aha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:45.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:643831,645374}So that's what it's about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:47.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645833,647126}I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:48.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:647126,648043}You're staying, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:49.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:648043,649587}What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:50.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:649587,650921}Just don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:52.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:650921,652882}Take your time, Colin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:55.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654049,655134}Take my time…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:11:00.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656635,660389}If possible, I'd like\Nto take Lassie with us…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:02.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661515,662516}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:04.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:662516,664435}What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:05.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664435,665561}I'm sorry, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:07.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:665561,667188}Let's go, Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:09.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:667188,669940}Sorry for borrowing Lassie again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:11.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:669940,671901}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:21.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:679116,681869}Look how happy Lassie was,\Ngoing with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:24.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681869,684371}So, why did I have to stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:26.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:684371,686916}John, sometimes\Nyou are so dense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:28.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:686916,688209}Dense?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:29.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:688209,689919}Look…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:31.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:690169,691003}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:32.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:691003,692421}He's fallen in love?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:33.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692421,693839}Our Colin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:35.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693839,695090}There you have it.
Comment: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:47.89,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:707895,707895}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:56.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714235,716695}What kind of treasure is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:12:00.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:716695,720532}Don't tell me it's a chest\Nburied by pirates long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:03.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:720532,723244}Nope. It's something\Nmuch more ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:05.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723244,725996}It's worthless to most people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:08.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:725996,728666}But to me it's\Nan invaluable treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:729083,730876}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:14.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:730876,734213}There's no way it could've been\Na pirates' treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:15.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734213,735172}Are you disappointed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:16.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:735172,736090}Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:20.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736090,740177}I'm not helping you\Nbecause of the treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:25.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:744556,745474}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:28.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745474,748102}Wait, Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:36.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754233,756735}Must be nice,\Nlooking for treasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:40.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756735,760739}But who would suspect…\NDoes Colin really love Chris?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:42.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:760739,762783}She looked much older.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:45.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:763784,765494}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:47.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765494,767037}No daydreaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:48.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:767037,768622}You dingbat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:49.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:768622,769248}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:51.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:769248,771834}You never heard that in love,\Nage doesn't matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:54.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:771834,774545}I didn't it.\NI'm such a dingbat, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:56.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:775087,776422}Revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:12:58.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:776422,778549}Geez, now you've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:05.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:784430,785764}We climbed a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:08.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:786682,788767}Chris, are you sure\Nthis is the right way?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:12.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789226,792271}Yes. If we walk this way,\Nwe'll reach the summit soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:15.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:793522,795274}We're going all the way\Nto the summit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:20.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798694,800612}How are you holding up?\NAre you tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:22.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:800612,802698}I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:24.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:802698,804158}For now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:28.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:807369,808954}It's pushing pretty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:36.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814543,816253}John Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:39.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817921,819381}John Carraclough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:41.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:819381,821133}I have a question for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:43.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821133,823052}Y… Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:51.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830851,831894}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:53.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:831894,833937}There was a landslide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:55.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833937,835439}Oh, no…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:57.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835856,837941}We've come such a long way,\Nall for nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:08.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:846658,848410}Look at Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:09.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:848410,849661}We can climb here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:12.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849661,852998}See? We can reach\Nthe summit this way, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:16.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:853624,856168}But we can't climb like Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:18.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856168,858128}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:20.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858128,860923}I'll make holes with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:21.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:860923,861757}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:26.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:861757,866095}It'll take a bit of time,\Nso you can relax in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:27.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:866095,867262}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:51.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:889993,891662}Now climb up, Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:52.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891662,892329}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:57.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895749,897251}Don't look down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:15:00.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:897251,900337}Yes, exactly.\NYou can rest your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:08.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906260,908303}We have already reached the peak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:08.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:908303,908971}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:10.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:908971,910139}And now…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:11.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910139,911723}Let me take a look at the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:12.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:911723,912641}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:13.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:912641,913475}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:16.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:914685,916019}A compass!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:17.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:916019,917980}Now that's what I call\Na treasure hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:21.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:917980,921108}But I don't think the map\Nwill be all that helpful, to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:22.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921108,922651}No, quite the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:25.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:922651,925195}Over there is the lighthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:28.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:925195,928115}So the treasure\Nis to the northwest from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:32.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931076,932077}Let's look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:37.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:935372,937958}Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:44.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:943464,944923}What's up, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:50.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:948302,950220}The path is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:55.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951680,955267}The tide came in and the path\Ngot completely flooded.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:56.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955267,956477}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:58.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956477,958228}Somebody help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:16:00.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:958228,960898}The path got flooded!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:04.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962983,964693}There's no way they could hear us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:08.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965944,968405}Now isn't the best time\Nto look for treasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:11.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968947,971909}We have to think\Nabout the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:14.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972493,974536}Colin, can you swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:16.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974536,976872}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:19.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:977873,979708}Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:23.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981001,983795}Sooner or later,\NJohn and Sandy will help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:28.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:984254,988467}I hope it's sooner, otherwise\NI won't make it to my ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:32.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989468,992054}It's possible I won't be able\Nto return home either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:34.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:992054,994264}Anyway, I'll better get down, and…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:39.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995390,999186}I don't mind not going to Australia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:39.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:999186,999811}Chris?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:45.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001188,1005108}The treasure is\Na memory of my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.52,0:16:47.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005526,1007069}A memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:50.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007069,1010113}My mom died last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:56.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012616,1016537}Dad, rather than living in a house\Nfull of memories of my mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.53,0:16:59.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016537,1019790}chose to start a new life\Nin a foreign country.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:04.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020749,1024086}But personally I'd rather stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:06.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024086,1026421}I didn't tell it to my dad, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:07.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026421,1027047}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:14.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027756,1034805}So before leaving England, I decided\Nto look for something my mom left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:21.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034805,1041436}When I was little, mom and dad\Ncame here with me to play treasure hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:23.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041436,1043313}It was so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:26.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043313,1046817}We drew this map together with Mom\Nand I've been holding onto it till today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:30.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048402,1050821}Now Mom's no longer around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:33.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050821,1053323}In the end, I could never find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:38.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056785,1058745}Let's find it now, Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:39.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059329,1059997}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:42.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059997,1062708}This is such an important thing,\Nthat you cannot let go of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:45.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062708,1065627}But we have to think\Nabout how to get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:47.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065627,1067838}I will find a solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:50.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067838,1070465}So let's go, Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:52.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071592,1072384}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:05.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083770,1085606}North-west. North-west!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:07.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085606,1087399}Is this the way, Chris?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.39,0:18:08.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087399,1088900}Yeah, no mistake about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:15.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094573,1095532}Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:17.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095532,1097409}It was buried under that tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:19.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097868,1099286}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:21.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099286,1101246}It's just like I remembered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:22.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101246,1102914}– We've found it!\N– Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:28.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105250,1108629}I remember Mom planting it.\NLook how big it has grown!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:30.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108629,1110005}Let's dig.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:31.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1110005,1111256}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:46.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124853,1126938}Ah… It's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.39,0:18:49.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127397,1129608}I collected them\Ntogether with Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:52.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130651,1132653}There's something written there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:54.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132653,1134446}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:56.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134863,1136615}"My Dear Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:19:01.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136615,1141536}I can imagine a tenderhearted girl\Nnow reading this."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:10.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149002,1150170}Mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:18.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155967,1158637}I have to go to Australia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:20.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1158637,1160347}I shouldn't worry Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:24.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163600,1164351}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.26,0:19:27.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166269,1167396}Let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:35.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172818,1175445}With this, I won't drown.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:37.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175445,1177239}I'll swim and I'll call for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.23,0:19:39.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177239,1179116}I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.53,0:19:41.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179533,1181451}I'll go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:44.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181451,1184037}It will sink if we go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:46.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184037,1186123}We don't have the time\Nto make another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.12,0:19:47.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186123,1187082}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:49.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187082,1189084}I'll be fine.\NLeave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.45,0:19:50.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189459,1190585}Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:55.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193171,1195215}Do your best, Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:57.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195590,1197217}Faster… Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:19:58.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198093,1198802}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:03.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199177,1203181}If I don't hurry, Chris' ship\Nwill depart without her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:05.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203181,1205308}Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:07.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205517,1207436}Stop it, Colin Jones!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:09.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207436,1209146}Go back to the ground at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:11.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209146,1211189}Turn! Turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:12.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211189,1212899}I'll go help you in a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.40,0:20:14.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213400,1214192}We're saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:17.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214359,1217195}Don't swim any further!\NWe'll get to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:22.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1218321,1222200}The ship bound for Australia\Nis about to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:23.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222200,1223410}Don't be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:24.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223410,1224703}I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.45,0:20:27.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225454,1227330}There's not much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:28.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227330,1228874}Say goodbye to her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:29.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228874,1229708}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:33.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1231668,1233628}Chris, uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:35.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233628,1235130}You're okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:36.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1235130,1236798}With going to Australia and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:41.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236798,1241470}Yes. Colin, thanks to you,\NI recovered my precious keepsake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.47,0:20:42.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241470,1242596}Thank you, Colin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:50.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1248059,1250270}Thank you, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:54.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1252481,1254691}Goodbye, John and Sandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:55.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1254691,1255776}Goodbye, Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:57.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1255776,1257027}Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:00.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1258487,1260530}Goodbye, Colin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:06.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1264534,1266244}Chris! Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.41,0:21:09.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1266411,1269748}Colin! I will never forget\Nwhat happened today!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:12.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1269956,1272501}Me neither! Me neither!\NI will never forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:15.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1272501,1275045}Goodbye! Goodbye, Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:17.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1275545,1277798}Goodbye… Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:20.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1279341,1280801}And away she goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.80,0:21:24.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1280801,1284971}So, did you find the treasure?\NWhat was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.97,0:21:25.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1284971,1285847}I'm sorry, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:28.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1286765,1288683}I can't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:30.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1288683,1290435}It's our little secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:34.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1293313,1294189}Colin…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:36.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1294523,1296149}Right, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:38.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1296149,1298193}Children, get ready to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:40.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1298735,1300403}Pff, how boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:45.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1301404,1305408}We have to go back.\NThe cart is already waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:47.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1305408,1307702}What?!
