Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:02.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1319506,1322342}{\i1}An influenza epidemic\Nhas spread in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:04.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1322342,1324719}{\i1}Even my father got sick\Nand stayed at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.71,0:22:08.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1324719,1328515}{\i1}Every day, Mom looks more tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.51,0:22:10.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1328515,1330100}{\i1}I hope she'll be okay…
